#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/byos/byos-overview.adoc:8
msgid ""
"{byos} instances make it easier to manage extensions such as ``LTSS`` or "
"``kernel live-patching``.  Extensions for PAYG instances can only be used in "
"conjunction with {productname}."
