#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The {productname} {payg} instance offers a flexible solution tailored to the "
"modern business landscape.  Key benefits include:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Cost Efficiency:* Pay only for what you use, aligning costs with the actual system management needs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "*No Subscription Required:* Eliminate the need for ongoing commitments or long-term subscriptions, allowing for budget flexibility.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Ease of Use:* Utilize {productname}'s powerful features on a **{payg}** or **{payglongform}** basis, streamlining initial setup and ongoing systems management.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Scalability:* Easily scale the number of systems managed according to your requirements, without worrying about subscription limitations.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "*Rapid Deployment:* Quickly run the image of your choice and begin managing your systems, enhancing responsiveness to your needs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/public-cloud-guide/payg/payg-overview.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
