#. type: Plain text
#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/salt/salt-yomi.adoc:19
msgid ""
"Adds a new configuration file called ``yomi-formula.conf`` in the [path]``/"
"etc/salt/master.d/`` directory.  This configuration file defines the Python "
"module and Salt states required by Yomi."
