#: modules/specialized-guides/pages/salt/salt-yomi.adoc:33
msgid ""
"The package installs a standard PXE OEM image generated by Kiwi, the initial "
"kernel and initrd in the [path]``/srv/pxe-yomi-image/`` directory, and the "
"second stage kernel, initrd and image in the [path]``/srv/pxe-yomi-image/"
"image`` directory."
